{"ts":"2026-07-09T20:53:09.046Z","author":"codex-root-20260709","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/6","value":{"created_at":"2026-07-09T20:53:09.045Z","author":"codex-root-20260709","text":"PR #487 CodeRabbit/Greptile review: protected the structural baseline from runtime signal injection, removed the context-evaluation SDK module's reverse dependency on CLI command types via dedicated public read contracts, made pressure parsing tolerant and batch-parsed time once, and made the public SDK example project-relative. Hot-path verification confirmed active service lookup is an in-memory registry check with no file I/O. Full coverage remains exact 100%."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-09T20:53:09.046Z"}],"before_hash":"0ab288d55bdf7eb30f62188805b0e4d87c71d1d64d5a2a2b61b97d389140d080","after_hash":"6e74c45c6ad366e7fc261081f18ab61764bdb8aa797c7ab5f8398e9fd27ad56f"}
{"ts":"2026-07-09T21:07:15.375Z","author":"codex-gpt5","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/7","value":{"created_at":"2026-07-09T21:07:15.375Z","author":"codex-gpt5","text":"Review evidence: implemented Gemini's final metadata-shape hardening on the current PR head. Ranking now accepts deadline values supplied as ISO strings, Date objects, or epoch numbers; normalizes risk labels case-insensitively after trimming; and ignores non-string assignee values safely. Added focused runtime tests, including malformed extension metadata. Verification: focused context-relevance tests, typecheck, ESLint, static quality gate, and full sandboxed repository coverage all pass: 270 files, 5,502 tests, exact 100% statements (34,300/34,300), branches (24,511/24,511), functions (6,873/6,873), and lines (32,967/32,967)."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-09T21:07:15.375Z"}],"before_hash":"6e74c45c6ad366e7fc261081f18ab61764bdb8aa797c7ab5f8398e9fd27ad56f","after_hash":"413d906c18c9aae8e917c6e99d87fc6e8d9f8a17d2be794bcb9dfeaa88827540"}
